        "description": "SYNCCORP proudly presents 'Experience Mecca.' The first true virtual reality experience from the Middle East. We will take you in a tour around the major landmarks of the holy place, offering you a gravitating, immersive look of the rituals. Built and designed with the utmost attention to details, Experience Mecca, is going to give you a real taste of what it's like to be in the most sacred and appreciated place in the Islamic world.\n\nHow does it feel?\n\nSimply, it's breathtaking. Once geared up, you'll be transported to the grand mosque, facing the Kaaba up close and personal. Muslim worshipers from different races, ethnics and countries are practicing the Tawaf, moving around the Kaaba in a perfect sync, representing all the meanings of harmony, peace and equality.\nThe emotions you will get are indescribable, you definitely have to see it, to believe it. So, sit back, relax and put your goggles on for a rare out of the body spiritual journey.",
